OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBecoming
OL,6,Frather cloudy during the evening,
OL,7,Fwhich might lead to the odd spot of
OL,8,Frain or drizzle over the western hills
OL,9,Flater in the night. Warmer than the
OL,10,Fprevious night and feeling humid too.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FMainly fine but on the cloudy
OL,13,Fside, with patches of light rain
OL,14,Fmoving in from the west during the
OL,15,Fafternoon. However, some areas may
OL,16,Fstay dry throughout. Staying warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
