OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FA
OL,6,Fchance of early showers or
OL,7,Fthunderstorms clearing east on Tuesday
OL,8,Fbut mostly dry and sunny otherwise.
OL,9,FWidely very warm, including at night.
OL,10,FChance of thundery showers developing
OL,11,Flater Thursday.
